{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>HUNT ME</strong> is a co-op <strong>horror</strong> survival game for 1-4 players. Gather the ingredients for the ritual, weaken the threat and banish it.  Be careful, you're also the prey!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/infrared_gif.gif?t=1735724544\" />Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Gameplay that's easy to master. <br>- Use your hunter's vision to target the threat. <br>- Move around it or confront it with your infrared light. <br>- Collect the ingredients for the ritual. <br>- Banish it! <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/gif02.gif?t=1735724544\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Replayability</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The locations of ritual objects, creatures, traps, safe spots and bones are randomly generated. AI behaviour is influenced by the player's actions and location - they're unpredictable! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/banish_gif.gif?t=1735724544\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Difficulty</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are 6 difficulty levels and a 100% customizable mode. You can discover the game at your own pace. The highest level requires strategy, responsiveness and mastery of the environment.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026770/extras/skill_gif.gif?t=1735724544\" />Co-op 1 to 4 players</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hunt as a team in multiplayer mode. But don't forget, you're also prey!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Solo game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">HUNT ME can be played solo. You'll need a more sophisticated strategy. There's no room for error!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[